Tyrael: Alright, boys. I will meet Cygnar in 24 hours. I want 
everything organized by then. First, Cheetah, find where the heck Vlad 
is. Second, I want the shields back at 100% efficiency. I'll do some 
work on the turrets. You have 12 hours to complete this.

He goes outside and takes a look at the turrets. Of the six, four had 
sustained damage. One of these had started overheating during the 
battle, while the three others had simply been shot at. Transforming 
to phoenix mode, Tyrael goes and replaces some parts in the heated 
one.
